{"tid":2262301,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"建制狙擊612基金 促規管網上眾籌","createTime":"2020-10-29T04:20:04.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-30T14:21:29.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"211e9f2e2412f5cc3705f7e20324a98948e5b872","tid":2262301,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T04:20:04.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201029/6ITYJIR6IBARPL3H2PFXUM3CHQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201029%2F6ITYJIR6IBARPL3H2PFXUM3CHQ%2F&d=2u41qa%2Bce9Gslgrzp%2F5Kil8MSy0xNzs2bKpftArA8vk%3D&h=2ebba0a0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201029%2F6ITYJIR6IBARPL3H2PFXUM3CHQ%2F&h=29ef9ddc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201029/6ITYJIR6IBARPL3H2PFXUM3CHQ/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n建制狙擊612基金 促規管網上眾籌<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/b5npYiywwsOnedPWXAMuorHCQu8=/1328x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/YWNJV2YJGNEV7CRPUNCJ2HWWHA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fb5npYiywwsOnedPWXAMuorHCQu8%3D%2F1328x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FYWNJV2YJGNEV7CRPUNCJ2HWWHA.jpg&h=0e8fae2f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n麥美娟<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】民主派及社運人士過去一年成功以網上眾籌，集合民間資源發起各種抗爭及法律行動，工聯會麥美娟昨透過立法會口頭質詢，試圖狙擊民主派經常進行網上眾籌，更將矛頭指向612基金等協助抗爭者的網上眾籌，要求政府規管。 財經事務及庫務局長許正宇回應指，若網上眾籌涉及非法目的、詐騙等，政府會規管，不存在「冇王管」。<br />\n<br />\n麥美娟昨日發言針對涉及反送中網上眾籌，她引用中共黨媒《人民日報》網站內容，指「攬炒派眾籌嘅錢去咗邊度？」麥美娟批評，透過眾籌不用向政府交稅和交報告，「好過出糧」，要求政府規管。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n許正宇：不存在冇王管<br />\n<br />\n同屬工聯會的陸頌雄接力狙擊，指政府對「黃獨黑」資金供應鏈放軟手腳，例如612基金請市民再捐款，他認為是「籌款、抗爭、法律」服務「一條龍」的黃色經濟圈，。。。。。。。。。。。。。，不存在「冇王管」，但指不同環節有不同形式的監管，警方若有需要會調查和起訴。他又指政府沒計劃將規管慈善機構等籌募捐款的法例，擴展至網上眾籌。"},{"pid":"a3f93bab13d1cd9f866c58f36ebc9cfadac3a16f","tid":2262301,"uid":211110,"like":1,"dislike":20,"score":-19,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T04:21:15.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e829571ecc63e78f45ceee50321f4d1bf0e98f8d","tid":2262301,"uid":45708,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T04:21:16.000Z","msg":"好多手足比612幫過，即係冇周圍講出嚟"},{"pid":"e6733b7701bf8aadca6cfb33cc877cb9bb19d54c","tid":2262301,"uid":161726,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T04:22:37.000Z","msg":"查下中聯辦同民建聯D 錢先啦"},{"pid":"9118fbc1ff9873cd373648537fc447ba269f2d5c","tid":2262301,"uid":124,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T04:23:00.000Z","msg":"連登依家咁多五毛 <br />\n唔係五毛就玩膠毒撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e1bf749488410bb1f27cdb8374ee2995d970eed","tid":2262301,"uid":332417,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T04:24:55.000Z","msg":"張相<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee8b5d0c896f1ad1e4e34e451bbfbf68931c7408","tid":2262301,"uid":11291,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T04:26:29.000Z","msg":"講還講唔好貼相<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9ee1a97d411a9be3874df193394314aff42c85b","tid":2262301,"uid":258948,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T04:26:32.000Z","msg":"個個女仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dllm.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc51826d29d779ff20b9676cd94c8830372873fd","tid":2262301,"uid":104719,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"a3f93bab13d1cd9f866c58f36ebc9cfadac3a16f","tid":2262301,"uid":211110,"like":1,"dislike":20,"score":-19,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T04:21:15.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTi